  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nI would like a flag on the validator client that allows me to specify where the slashing database file is written. This would allow me to separate the slashing database from sensitive keystore data. \r\n\r\n## Version\r\n\r\nN/A\r\n\r\n## Present Behaviour\r\n\r\nCurrently, the database is written to the validators dir, which also contains the definitions file and keystore data.\r\n\r\n## Expected Behaviour\r\n\r\nThe flag would allow the database to written to a location of my choosing.\r\n\r\n## Steps to resolve\r\n\r\nN/A\r\n",
